General Information

VIERRA is a dedicated inner beauty brand endeavour of evidence-based product research & development, to provide a holistic approach for beautiful skin, health & wellbeing. The VIERRA RESVERATROL GRAPE SUPREME ESSENCE is a plant-based detox & antioxidant superfood beauty liquid with prebiotics for weight management, energy level, radiant skin & digestive health. The Resveratrol beauty liquid pack of all the powerful anti-ageing science into the formula. The breakthrough super small molecule form allows active ingredients including resveratrol, arbutin and prebiotic to nourish your skin cell for advanced antioxidant, skin beauty & detox support!

Directions

Adult-one serve a day. Can be taken as one pouch concentrate or diluted with up to 250ml of chilled water,keep the liquid under your tongue for 10 seconds for better nutrient absorption.
